{"title":"清明","authors":["吴兵"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"清明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑，是一部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数人用鲜血合著的教科书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个棱角分明的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝固了一片片硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个血气方刚的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因抖开那面戳破黑暗的战旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而抖开了黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热乎乎的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芳草青青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但割断过呼吸的弹片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍没有腐烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺耳的呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着鲜花盛开的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐入多雨的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满头白发的母亲，来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她永远忘不了儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了那些与儿子一样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她曾为他们补过很多补钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在她有很多的新衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲站住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一群举臂宣誓的红领巾前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她，又看到了自己的儿子"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}